106
00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:23.520
we have clinical experience,

107
00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:24.870
and we have randomized control trials.

108
00:05:24.870 --> 00:05:28.800
These are all the types or sources of evidence

109
00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:32.010
from which we're trying to make clinical decisions.

110
00:05:32.010 --> 00:05:36.450
Now, when we come down to looking at observational studies

111
00:05:36.450 --> 00:05:38.400
