Now it comes into play of course in meta analysis as well.

114
00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:46.380
But different methods are used

115
00:05:46.380 --> 00:05:49.050
depending on the type of study that you have.

116
00:05:49.050 --> 00:05:50.910
Now, I wanna remind you with our strength

117
00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:51.998
of recommendation taxonomy,

118
00:05:51.998 --> 00:05:55.438
because there will be a question on the exam on this.

119
00:05:55.438 --> 00:05:59.397
The question is not going to be this recommendation

