00:13:39.540 --> 00:13:40.560
a number needed to screen,

286
00:13:40.560 --> 00:13:43.410
which is just like calculate the number needed to treat.

287
00:13:43.410 --> 00:13:44.460
The number needed to harm

288
00:13:44.460 --> 00:13:45.510
and the number needed to treat

289
00:13:45.510 --> 00:13:47.850
actually you will see is an inverse of one another.

290
00:13:47.850 --> 00:13:50.033
And we'll take a look at that in just a moment.

291
00:13:50.910 --> 00:13:53.096
So that's how we gotta set up the table

292
00:13:53.096 --> 00:13:57.720
to use those equations for measuring risk.

293
00:13:57.720 --> 00:13:58.800
Everybody with me still?

294
00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:00.600
Nod your head.

