300
00:14:12.210 --> 00:14:14.313
We haven't done any math yet, okay.

301
00:14:15.570 --> 00:14:18.778
So let's start by looking at a cohort study.

302
00:14:18.778 --> 00:14:20.541
What are we talking about here?

303
00:14:20.541 --> 00:14:23.070
Well, we got a population,

304
00:14:23.070 --> 00:14:24.224
and in that population,

305
00:14:24.224 --> 00:14:26.520
people are either disease free

306
00:14:26.520 --> 00:14:28.500
or they got the disease we're looking at.

307
00:14:28.500 --> 00:14:29.493
Whatever it is.

308
00:14:30.450 --> 00:14:34.560
We're really interested in a prospective study of saying,

309
00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:37.143
okay, let me find the disease free people.

310
00:14:39.450 --> 00:14:41.850
They're gonna be exposed to some factor.

