00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:19.620
and then retrospectively go back and say,

327
00:15:19.620 --> 00:15:21.630
I'm concerned that maybe this was the factor

328
00:15:21.630 --> 00:15:23.520
that it caused this.

329
00:15:23.520 --> 00:15:25.350
Were you exposed or not exposed to it?

330
00:15:25.350 --> 00:15:26.430
Then how much were you exposed,

331
00:15:26.430 --> 00:15:28.260
not exposed, et cetera, et cetera.

332
00:15:28.260 --> 00:15:30.930
So cohort studies can be done either prospectively

333
00:15:30.930 --> 00:15:35.930
if it's a relatively common outcome like having a baby,

334
00:15:36.120 --> 00:15:38.820
or it can be done retrospectively,

335
00:15:38.820 --> 00:15:43.820
