00:15:55.020 --> 00:16:00.020
But sometimes you need to do it prospectively

341
00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:03.930
and see what happens.

342
00:16:03.930 --> 00:16:07.020
You know, a good example of a prospective study,

343
00:16:07.020 --> 00:16:10.110
