00:16:49.020 --> 00:16:51.840
So that was a prospective cohort study to look at,

357
00:16:51.840 --> 00:16:53.440
did it make a difference or not?

358
00:16:55.020 --> 00:16:56.340
They didn't vary what you ate,

359
00:16:56.340 --> 00:16:58.380
they just said, did you get better?

360
00:16:58.380 --> 00:17:03.380
Okay, now here's an example we're gonna use.

